sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio IngressGateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant VS as VirtualService<br/>Routing
    participant Knative as Knative/Istio Routing<br/>mTLS optional
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant EventBroker as Knative Eventing Broker<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,EventBroker: Flow 1: Model Deployment and Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>VS: Forward HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    VS->>Knative: Route via VirtualService<br/>mTLS (optional via Istio)

    Note over Predictor: On first request, pod may scale from zero

    Note over Predictor,Storage: Init Container: storage-initializer
    Predictor->>Storage: Download Model Artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/GCP SA/Azure creds
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model Files

    Knative->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token (optional)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run Inference
    Predictor-->>Knative: Prediction Result<br/>JSON Response
    Knative-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    opt Logging Enabled
        Predictor->>EventBroker: Send Request/Response Logs<br/>HTTP, TLS via Istio (optional)
    end

    Note over Client,EventBroker: Flow 2: InferenceGraph Multi-Model Pipeline

    participant Router as InferenceGraph Router<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Step1 as Preprocessor Service<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Step2 as Predictor Service<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Step3 as Postprocessor Service<br/>8000/TCP

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/pipeline:predict<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Router: Forward via VirtualService<br/>mTLS (optional via Istio)

    Router->>Step1: Step 1: Preprocess<br/>mTLS (optional), Bearer Token (propagated)
    Step1-->>Router: Preprocessed Data

    Router->>Step2: Step 2: Predict<br/>mTLS (optional), Bearer Token (propagated)
    Step2-->>Router: Prediction

    Router->>Step3: Step 3: Postprocess<br/>mTLS (optional), Bearer Token (propagated)
    Step3-->>Router: Final Result

    Router-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,EventBroker: Flow 3: LLM Disaggregated Inference

    participant LLMRouter as LLM Router<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Scheduler as LLM Scheduler<br/>9003/TCP gRPC
    participant Prefill as Prefill Worker<br/>LeaderWorkerSet
    participant Decode as Decode Worker<br/>LeaderWorkerSet

    Client->>Gateway: POST /openai/v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>LLMRouter: Forward via VirtualService<br/>mTLS (optional)

    LLMRouter->>Scheduler: Schedule Request<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, mTLS (optional)

    Scheduler->>Prefill: Prefill Phase<br/>HTTP/gRPC, mTLS (optional)
    Prefill-->>Scheduler: KV Cache

    Scheduler->>Decode: Decode Phase<br/>HTTP/gRPC, mTLS (optional)
    Decode-->>Scheduler: Token Stream

    Scheduler-->>LLMRouter: Streaming Response
    LLMRouter-->>Gateway: Streaming Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Streaming Response
